---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Stone Bicycle Coalition blog - News, stories, and updates from our community bike co-op.
activeNav: blog
---

<section class="page-header">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p>News, stories, and updates from our community</p>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="blog-list">
            {% if wp.posts.length > 0 %}
                {% for post in wp.posts %}
                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);"></div>
                    <div class="blog-card-content">
                        <div class="blog-card-meta">
                            <time>{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2><a href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/">{{ post.title }}</a></h2>
                        <p>{{ post.excerpt | truncate(200) }}</p>
                        <a href="/blog/{{ post.slug }}/" class="read-more">Read More &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
                {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: var(--color-primary);"></div>
                    <div class="blog-card-content">
                        <div class="blog-card-meta">
                            <time>March 31, 2026</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2>AEP Grant Awarded!</h2>
                        <p>Big news — Stone Bicycle Coalition has been awarded a $1,000 grant from the American Empathy Project! This funding supports our Pedal for Empathy community ride on May 2nd.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="blog-card">
                    <div class="blog-card-image" style="background-color: var(--color-secondary);"></div>
                    <div class="blog-card-content">
                        <div class="blog-card-meta">
                            <time>March 25, 2026</time>
                        </div>
                        <h2>Free Bikes Seeking Riders</h2>
                        <p>We have bikes available for anyone who needs reliable transportation. Refurbished with care, tuned up, and ready to ride.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
